      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, thanks. I'm a little worried though, some people in the local Facebook groups have been kinda vocal about DEI stuff lately, saying it's just political stuff and doesn't belong in a small business. \n\nCan you give me a few more options that feel a bit more... I don't know, impactful? Maybe something that explains why we're doing this or why it's actually important for the bakery's future?",
